strings:
<voice_0x01000EF2><se_def>Prince Charmles: Look! There's one!
An Argon lizard!
It's sound asleep, too!
<voice_0x01000EF3><se_def>Prince Charmles: Now then, <leader>, do you suppose you could lure it out somehow?
<voice_0x01000EF8><se_def>Prince Charmles: We could try enticing it with a salamango, I suppose, but maybe we're a bit too far away here?
